S"Why is TweetCaster the #1 Twitter app? At 4.4 stars, no other Twitter app has a higher user rating, even the official Twitter app. When it comes to Twitter apps, you have lots of choices. So why not choose the best? Why do over 6 million users love TweetCaster?  * Beauty, Speed, Reliability \xe2\x80\x93 TweetCaster has a gorgeous look with an intuitive interface that makes it super easy to navigate and use.  Plus it\xe2\x80\x99s lightning fast, and ultra reliable.* Amazing Features \xe2\x80\x93 Optimized for both phones and tablets, TweetCaster\xe2\x80\x99s innovative feature set has been highly praised by users and reviewers. TweetCaster Exclusives:* Search Party \xe2\x80\x93 How Twitter search was meant to be! Lets you search just your own timeline, or someone else\xe2\x80\x99s, rather than all of Twitter.* My Stats \xe2\x80\x93 Up-to-the-minute tally of stats includes Most Retweeted, Most Mentioned, Most Favorited, many more* Zip It \xe2\x80\x93 Zip annoying tweeters or keywords from your timeline without unfollowing * SmartLists \xe2\x80\x93 Hands down, the simplest and best way to use Twitter Lists * Photo Effects \xe2\x80\x93 Add cool filters, effects and captions to photos, as you upload them* Speak Tweets \xe2\x80\x93 Tap microphone on New Tweet screen to speak instead of typing* Enhanced Widget \xe2\x80\x93 Updated widget is scrollable and resizeable (Android 3.0+)! * Smart Filters \xe2\x80\x93 Filter your timeline to look only at tweets with photos, links or videosEven More Features:* Facebook \xe2\x80\x93 Simultaneously post to Twitter and Facebook * Multiple Twitter Accounts \xe2\x80\x93 Manage and easily post to multiple Twitter accounts* Schedule Tweets \xe2\x80\x93 Compose a tweet and send later, using Buffer* TweetMarker \xe2\x80\x93 Use to keep your place in the timeline across multiple devices* Read Later \xe2\x80\x93 Save links to read/view later using Pocket or Instapaper* Readability \xe2\x80\x93 View links in Readability mode for a mobile-optimized view* Themes \xe2\x80\x93 Twelve vibrant, colorful themes* Color Code Tweets \xe2\x80\x93 Choose a custom color for your Tweets and mentions* Multiple widgets \xe2\x80\x93 Bring TweetCaster to your home screen with customizable widgets* Long Tweets \xe2\x80\x93 Use Twitlonger service to tweet over 140 characters* Who to Follow \xe2\x80\x93 Suggests people to followWhat People are Saying:\xe2\x80\x9cThis is the best Twitter app I've found. Very easy to use and very beautiful.\xe2\x80\x9d \xe2\x80\x93 Che, TweetCaster User (v6.8) \xe2\x80\x9cExcellent Twitter client.\xe2\x80\x9d \xe2\x80\x93 TUAW\xe2\x80\x9cContender for best Twitter app. 5/5 bars.\xe2\x80\x9d \xe2\x80\x93 Appolicious\xe2\x80\x9cNicely designed\xe2\x80\xa6 Colorful but clean.\xe2\x80\x9d \xe2\x80\x93 CNETkeywords: Twitter, tweet, smartphone, tablet, Android, facebook, news, zip, phone, social, network, media, best, topRecent changes:- Instagram image preview support updated- Tweets you favorite or retweet are now marked with an indicator icon- Added preview support for Telly videos- Improved ability to auto-complete usernames when composing a tweet- Smart Filter added to individual user's mentions and favorites"
